post_text:
Message from Superintendent Dr. Chris Pearson;

As we move into Spring, there is often a heightened anxiety around our state test. Please know that here at Conway we care about the education of the whole-child. Not only do we want our students to be good at reading and math, but also to be imaginative, kind and responsible citizens who love learning.

This is our commitment to our students, a commitment that we try to live every day.

