post_text:
Message from Superintendent Dr. Chris Pearson;

I would like to take this opportunity to say thank you to the Conway Classified Staff Members who dedicate themselves every day to our students. We are very fortunate to have such professional, capable and caring paraprofessionals, cooks, custodians, bus drivers and office administrators. All of you contribute mightily to the special environment that is the Conway School District.

Thank you!!

